我本来能说 真不该问你
I'd say I'm sorry I asked,

5
00:00:11,870 --> 00:00:14,130
可是我没问
except I didn't.

6
00:00:14,130 --> 00:00:16,570
哦 你看 这期科学美国人
Oh, look, it's the Scientific American

7
00:00:16,570 --> 00:00:19,380
报道了Leonard和我写的那篇论文
that covered the paper Leonard and I wrote.

8
00:00:19,380 --> 00:00:21,350
哦 让我看看
Oh, let me see.

9
00:00:21,350 --> 00:00:23,980
我对接受采访的态度很复杂
I have mixed feelings about doing interviews.

10
00:00:23,990 --> 00:00:26,150
我喜欢自己说话
I like the part where I talk.

11
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:29,830
但是我不喜欢听别人说话
I do not like the part where the other man talks.

12
00:00:31,230 --> 00:00:34,100
Sheldon 这篇文章一点都没有提到Leonard
Sheldon, this article doesn't mention Leonard at all.

13
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:35,870
