Well, that can't be right.

14
00:00:35,870 --> 00:00:38,940
它上面只写了"Cooper博士和他的团队"
It only refers to "Dr. Cooper and his team."

15
00:00:38,950 --> 00:00:40,840
你谈到过他吗?
Did you even talk about him?

16
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:43,420
我只是回答了几个关于这个理论的问题
All I did was answer a few questions about the theory.

17
00:00:43,420 --> 00:00:45,580
我还感谢了科学美国人
And then expressed my gratitude that Scientific American

18
00:00:45,590 --> 00:00:49,050
没有寄来那些臭臭的香水卡片
doesn't include any of those smelly perfume cards.

19
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:51,690
Leonard真可怜
Poor Leonard.

20
00:00:51,690 --> 00:00:54,020
为什么? 他想出来的理论
Why? The theory he came up with

21
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:55,690
被科学美国人报道了
just got mentioned in Scientific American.

22
00:00:55,690 --> 00:00:57,050
他应该很兴奋啊
He ought to be thrilled.

23
00:00:57,060 --> 00:00:58,490
他也许不会
He might not be.

24
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,530
哦 也许你说的对
Oh, maybe you're right.

25
00:01:00,530 --> 00:01:02,860
他是有点笨笨的
He is kind of a lump.

26
00:01:02,860 --> 00:01:04,000
你自己想想看
Think about it.

27
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,930
如果他们说你是Leonard的团队里的一员
How would you feel if you were referred to

28
00:01:05,930 --> 00:01:07,640
你会怎么想?
as part of Leonard's team?

29
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,900
哦 我会非常生气的
Oh, I'd be incensed.

30
00:01:09,910 --> 00:01:12,410
那你明白我想说什么了吗?
So you see what I'm getting at?

31
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:14,980
吱吱叫的轮子有油加?
Squeaky wheel gets the grease?

32
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,380
不是
No.

33
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:18,290
这山望着那山高?
Grass is always greener?

34
00:01:18,290 --> 00:01:19,990
再试试
Try again.

35
00:01:19,990 --> 00:01:21,650
啊 我不知道... 我们都是树精格鲁特?
Well, I don't know... we're all Groot?

36
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:23,760
告诉我吧
Just tell me.

37
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,830
Leonard和你对这份论文的贡献一样大
Leonard is as much a part of this paper

38
00:01:25,830 --> 00:01:27,900
而他被忽视了
as you are, and he was overlooked.

39
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,860
他会很难过的
He's going to feel bad.

40
00:01:29,870 --> 00:01:32,140
但这不是我的错啊
But it wasn't my fault.

41
00:01:32,140 --> 00:01:33,670
我又没有把他排除出去
I didn't exclude him.

42
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:35,270
这篇文章也不是我写的
And I didn't write the article.

43
00:01:35,270 --> 00:01:38,340
你还记得你在迪士尼乐园那次 他们没有选你
Remember that time you didn't get picked to pull the sword out

44
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:41,570
去拔石中剑 而是挑了另外一个小孩吗?
of the stone at Disneyland and they let that other kid do it?

45
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,780
哦 那小屁孩!
Oh, that kid!

46
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:50,030
Leonard真可怜
Poor Leonard.

47
00:01:50,030 --> 00:01:51,830
是啊
Exactly.

48
